denial_opening.speaker: internal
denial_opening.line: Everything is fine. Nothing is wrong. I refuse to acknowledge it. It is not a problem. I am fine. Everyone is here. Everyone is okay.

denial_opening.speaker: dad
denial_opening.line: Are you going to be okay?

denial_opening.speaker: self
denial_opening.line: Yes. I don't have any problems. I am perfectly fine.

anger_opening.speaker: internal
anger_opening.line: YOU CAN'T TAKE HER AWAY FROM ME I WILL KILL YOU I WILL I SWEAR I HATE YOU I WILL KILL YOU YOU ARE

bargaining_1.speaker: internal
bargaining_1.line: We could have taken her to the hospital sooner. She could have lived had we gone to the doctor. We should have seen the signs.

bargaining_2.speaker: internal
bargaining_2.line: I'll do anything. Bring her back and I'll give you anything you want.

bargaining_3.speaker: internal
bargaining_3.line: God, bring her back, and I'll never do anything wrong again. Give me her back and I'll never go to church. I'll never do anything wrong. Give me her back.

bargaining_4.speaker: internal
bargaining_4.line: Please, I'm begging you, give her back to me.

bargaining_5.speaker: internal
bargaining_5.line: Tell me what you want! Please, I'll give it to you. Please give her back.

acceptance_opening.speaker: dad
acceptance_opening.line: You seem to be feeling better now.
